{"tid":443792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞女天慈邨被強姦　重案閃電拉26歲本地男","createTime":"2017-10-22T02:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T03:40:20.000Z","uid":20058,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1b475a67ac137a845d55255d20305ea00bfdaa72","tid":443792,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T02:35:36.000Z","msg":"淫魔天水圍強姦南亞女，警方重案組不足12小時擒獲涉案男。昨日上午11時許，一名25歲南亞裔女子，於天喜街天慈邨報警，稱在上址一單位被一名男子強姦。警方接報到場，將女事主送院檢查，經初步調查，案件列強姦，交由元朗警區重案組第3隊跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n重案組探員翻看現場天眼片段及蒐證後，鎖定一名目標，至昨晚10時30分，於天水圍拘捕一名26歲姓馮男子，他涉嫌「強姦」，帶署通宵扣查。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171022/mobile/bkn-20171022020040141-1022_00822_001.html?eventPath=hk_news&amp;eventID=402883475f329d20015f3f58032d7b76\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171022%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171022020040141-1022_00822_001.html%3FeventPath%3Dhk_news%26eventID%3D402883475f329d20015f3f58032d7b76&d=cCi23bzN%2B4inYYHu1032Qdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=05179e8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171022/mobile/bkn-20171022020040141-1022_00822_001.html?eventPath=hk_news&amp;eventID=402883475f329d20015f3f58032d7b76</a>"},{"pid":"5f894c088009312fc786818031b724a0ffa1ba18","tid":443792,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T02:36:21.000Z","msg":"以眼還眼"},{"pid":"cdd1d45df1cb423aa224ee96fa3d50fb5924c77d","tid":443792,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我最想見到既畫面<br />\n有反彈係好事"},{"pid":"5212b9ac5e3983bf47ca526907f02524f9b2ba94","tid":443792,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T02:38:52.000Z","msg":"南亞狗就咁快拉到人"},{"pid":"40ee1f799b0324a94a1249df057ffd022e4aa859","tid":443792,"uid":26752,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"辛苦佢囉蝻都夠膽屌<img src=\"